Task
Sum of even positive array elements
Write a function sumOfEvenPositive that takes the arr array as an argument and returns the sum of the even positive elements of the array.
Use a loop in your solution. Array methods are not allowed.
Example:
• function sumOfEvenPositive ([2, 2, 3, -2, - 4]) must return 4;
• function sumOfEvenPositive ([15, -13]) must return 0;
• the sumOfEvenPositive ([]) function must return 0.

Solution
function sumOfEvenPositive (arr) {
  let sum = 0;
   for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
     if (arr [i]% 2 === 0 && arr [i]> 0)
     sum = sum + arr [i];
   }
    return sum;
}
